parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure due to Radiator Coolant Leak
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. The mixing of coolant and transmission fluid can also cause damage to the transmission and other components, resulting in costly repairs.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power
vibration
or shuddering when accelerating
difficulty shifting gears
or complete loss of transmission function. The transmission may also produce a whining or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the dynamic control warning light may indicate a problem with the vehicle's transmission or other systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The dynamic control warning light may illuminate on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the vehicle's transmission or other systems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator can cause coolant to leak into the transmission, leading to transmission damage, stalling, and loss of power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience hesitation or stalling
especially when shifting gears
accompanied by a loud knocking or grinding noise. The transmission may slip or hesitate to engage
and the vehicle may vibrate or shake.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure Due to Radiator Coolant Contamination
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The contamination of the transmission fluid with radiator coolant can cause the transmission to fail, leading to costly repairs and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience hesitation or stalling
especially when shifting gears
accompanied by a loud knocking or grinding noise. The transmission may slip or hesitate to engage
and the vehicle may vibrate or shake.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Notification and Inadequate Warranty Coverage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of notification and inadequate warranty coverage can leave vehicle owners with costly repair bills and a sense of frustration and mistrust towards the manufacturer.
symptoms: Vehicle owners may not receive timely notification of potential issues or warranty extensions
leading to unexpected repair costs and potential safety risks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty fuel gauge sensor can cause the fuel gauge to display inaccurate readings, leading to unexpected fuel exhaustion, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The fuel gauge displays incorrect readings
the fuel gauge freezes at a certain level
the fuel gauge shows an empty tank when the tank is full
the fuel gauge shows a full tank when the tank is empty
the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator and transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the radiator coolant leaks into the transmission
the transmission fluid leaks out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent electrical problems can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The headlights turn on and off
the fan turns on and off
the anti-theft system locks the driver out
the vehicle will not start.
